long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The ultimate companion for Solario traders, with tools to improve the efficiency and profitability of trading limited items.

Solimons is a free extension designed to improve the limited item trading experience on solario.ws.

Solimons' features include:
• Values on Trading Window  - see Solimons item values and calculated totals displayed within your trading pages!
• Values on Catalog Page - view Solimons item values on the Catalog page, useful to snipe amazing deals and calculate purchases!

Join our Discord server and Solario group:
• https://discord.gg/PHjU6JC83J
• https://solario.ws/groups/12/Solimons

Solimons is not affiliated with roblox.com, rolimons.com or solario.ws.
